name: Virtuous-virology
tagline: Continuing the Virtuos Virology community from google+
body:
# Welcome to the world of good viruses! Which don't cause disease...

The idea was conceived by Totto Pastime and we paired up to start this community.
We're looking forward to sharing amazing viral news in this space! 

Keeping fingers crossed, and eager for more members who'd love to talk about the brighter side!!

Because life is all about positivity, and virtuousness!
